OL,3,CVictory for 'people power' as lido
OL,4,Cprepares to open
OL,6,FTeignmouth Lido will open for the
OL,7,Fsummer of 2026 after what campaigners
OL,8,Fare calling a victory for 'people
OL,9,Fpower'.
OL,11,FThe executive committee of Teignbridge
OL,12,FCouncil voted in February to sell the
OL,13,Foutdoor swimming pool and not to open
OL,14,Fit this season as part of plans to
OL,15,Fsave thousands of pounds a year.
OL,17,FCampaigners said it should be kept
OL,18,Fopen while arrangements were made to
OL,19,Fhand over the running of the site to
OL,20,Fthe community.
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/6
