OL,24,ANext Page BSW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,435,430,120,260,000,100
PN,43406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F434A1773245481
OL,3,CVictory for 'people power' as lido
OL,4,Cprepares to open
OL,6,F"What you're seeing is democracy in
OL,7,Faction," she said. "Teignbridge made a
OL,8,Fdecision based on insufficient
OL,9,Finformation, and when they got that
OL,10,Finformation from the public, they
OL,11,Fchanged their minds."
OL,13,FCredit: Guy Henderson, LDRS
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/6
